org.treetank.io.file
Class ByteBufferSinkAndSource

java.lang.Object
  org.treetank.io.file.ByteBufferSinkAndSource
All Implemented Interfaces:
ITTSink, ITTSource
public final class ByteBufferSinkAndSource
extends Object
implements ITTSink, ITTSource

This class represents the byte input/output mechanism for File-access. After all, it is just a simple wrapper for the ByteBuffer and exists only for convenience reasons.

Author:
Sebastian Graf, University of Konstanz
